Sure-Handed Alchemy		CATEGORY:FEAT		TYPE:General																PRESKILL:1,Craft (Alchemy)=3	PRETEXT:Craft (alchemy) 3 ranks.										DESC:Your steady hand increases your chances of success with spontaneous alchemy and reduces your number of mishaps.	SOURCEPAGE:p.5	BENEFIT:When attempting Craft (alchemy) checks to create items using spontaneous alchemy, you gain a cumulative +1 circumstance bonus for each distinct reagent called for by the recipe. A failed Craft (alchemy) check results in a mishap only on a natural 1 . Finally, you take no penalties on Craft (alchemy) checks when using improvised equipment to create items using spontaneous alchemy.
Toxicological Timing		CATEGORY:FEAT		TYPE:General																PRESKILL:1,Craft (Alchemy)=9	PRETEXT:Craft (alchemy) 9 ranks.										DESC:You know how to adjust the amount of time a poison takes to produce its effects.						SOURCEPAGE:p.8	BENEFIT:When you craft a poison with the Craft (alchemy) skill (whether using the normal Craft rules or the rules for spontaneous alchemy), you can increase or decrease the unit of time used to measure the frequency of a poison you craft by up to one step along the following scale: rounds, minutes, hours, days.
